Whales, pearls, and pretty native girls. Plenty of high-seas adventure is dished up as sailor Joel Shore goes looking for his whale hunter brother, Mark, who is lost during a disastrous mission at sea. Joel and his wife, Priscilla, eventually catch up with Mark on a tropical island.
